I learned a lot from this experience, i am not rich but i have an open heart and iam always ready to share my happiness with other people.

</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-35.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">2</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Volunteer Work</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Why is volunteering important?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Why is volunteering important ?
Because I think that from volunteer works i can make friends with other people, who are very kind and friendly. Volunteer works are meaningful. I can learn some lessons from it. For example, It does not matter if you are rich or poor, you can always share something with other people "sharing is caring".
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-35.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">3</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Volunteer Work</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Would you like to join a charity project?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> </p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-36.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Outdoor Activities</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Do you like outdoor activities?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you like outdoor activities? (hoạt động ngoài trời). 
-> Not entirely. 
+) If the weather is nice and i have free time i would like to join in outdoor activities like sports or pinic -> It is good for my health, i can explore to the nature -> From that, this helps me to relax and keep fit.
+) But, sometimes i want to stay at home to take care of and have more time with my family

</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-36.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">2</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Outdoor Activities</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Which activity is best for family?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Which activity is best for family?
-> Pinic is one of the greatest way to spend with family. Because on the pinic, we can relax on the towel, have some home-made dishes or explore the nature together, finally, take a photo this helps me to save memories last forever.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-36.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">3</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Outdoor Activities</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Is it good to spend time in nature?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Is it good to spend time in nature?
Yes, definitely. 
-> Because recently i live in big city, where is highly polluted and crowded. I want to have nicer place that can provide me a healthier environment like fresh air, many trees and no bustle (tiếng ồn) to relax. This can improve my health 
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-37.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Reading Habit</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">What kind of books do you read most?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What kind of books do you read most?
-> Recently i am a big fan of romantic books. Because my life is very boring but each book contains another life, where has new experiences and people. From that i can explore and learn new lessons. It is more interesting than my daily routine.   
like = get interested in = am fancinated by = am a big fan of
romantic (adj): ngôn tình.
comic (adj): 
comedy: hài 
academic (adj): học thuật</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-37.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">2</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Reading Habit</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Where is your favorite place to read?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Where is your favorite place to read?
-> My house is the favourite place to read. Because it is quite and private so i can focus on the books. Sometimes i can discuss about the book content with family members. This create memories last forever.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-37.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">3</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Reading Habit</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Should children read more books?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Should children read more books?
Lợi ích của sách
I agree that children should be promoted to read more books 
-> Because some books are meaningful. Each book containts new experiences, people and lessons so it can be inspiring for reader. 
-> I think reading books is a healthy hobby. It helps children to become more creative and knowledgable instead of spending too much time on mobile phone.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-38.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Gardening</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Do you like gardening?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you like gardening?
-> Not entirely. 
-> When i used to be a child. I had a lot of free time. Gaderning was one of my hobby. It is a healthy hobby. It helps me to be closer to nature and learn to take responsibility.
-> But recently, i had my works, so i pretty busy with my private life so i seldom do gardening.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-38.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">2</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Gardening</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">What is your favorite plant?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What is your favorite plant?
-> I think rose is my beloved one. 
because rose symbolizes love. It would be very romantic to receive a bouquet of flowers on special days like Woman days, Valentine. It reminds me that someone trully cares about me.
-> It is sunflower. 
+) because this plant always follow the sunlight. It always reminds me to look for the future and hope.  






</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-38.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">3</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Gardening</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Is gardening good for stress?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Is gardening good for stress?
Not entirely, 
Because gaderning is highly-demanding. It requires responsibilites. When you take care of anything, you need to spend time, money and effort on it. But some people are very busy with their works or they have no knowledge about it.   
However, for people who have gaderding as their hobby. This connect people with nature. It helps them healthier and happier.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-39.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Photography</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">How often do you take photos?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> How often do you take photos?
Seldom i take photo but only when i have outdoor activities like during summer trip, pinic, ... i will take some  of the natures and landscape. Especially, when i am with friends or family members. This create memories last forever.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-39.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">2</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Photography</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Do you prefer taking photos of people or nature?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you prefer taking photos of people or nature?
-> I prefer to take photos of people because i want save memories with friends and family members. It reminds of good memories. While, photos of nature i can see a thousands of those pictures on the Internet, and i can simply dowload it.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-39.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">3</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Photography</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Is a professional camera necessary?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Is a professional camera necessary (cần thiết) ?
Not entirely. 
professional camera is necessary. It helps you to take high-quality photos so it suitable with special days like wedding days, graduation, anniversary, ... 
However, in modern world, you can take a photo by phone, it is very convinient and cheap. You can take photo anywhere anytime without fees.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-40.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Pets Care</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Is it expensive to keep a pet?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Is it expensive to keep a pet?
I agree with that, if you have a pet, you have to take the responsibilites. You must pay for the services like healthcare, maintenance. You also have to pay for foods, water, shelter, vaccin
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-40.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">2</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Pets Care</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">What is the best pet for a small apartment?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What is the best pet for a small apartment?
-> cat and dog is one of the most famous animal to keep in small apartment. Because cat and dog is lovely and friendly.  
domestic (adj): nuôi trong nhà
tamed (adj): thuần hóa</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-40.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">3</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Pets Care</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Should children have pets?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Should children have pets?
Lợi ích:
Not entirely 
1. because when children have a pet, they have to take responsibilties to take care of it. But it is highly-demanding. It requires a lot of time, money and effort but children do not have enough resources. They are careless and have no knowledge. They can accidently kill the animal. 
2. However, if children have the support from family. Having pets can teach children love and responsibility.


</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-41.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Fitness</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">How do you stay fit?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> How do you stay fit?
1. I have to control my regular diet (thực đơn). eat more vegetable, eat less red meat, drink enough water, avoid fat food.
2. I should change my daily routine. do more excerices, go to sleep earlier, restrict stay up late.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-41.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">2</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Fitness</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Do you prefer gym or home workout?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you prefer gym or home workout?
I prefer gym. because in the gym, there many people, who do excercises, this inspire me. It also offers more equipments so i can train every parts of my body. Finally, i can ask for advices from personal trainer profesionally.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-41.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">3</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Fitness</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Is diet more important than exercise?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Is diet more important than exercise?
-> i think diet and excercise are equally important. They support each other. While diet helps you to control your weight, excercise improve your muscles.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-42.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Socializing</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Where do you like to meet friends?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Where do you like to meet friends?
I usually meet friends at the restaurant or coffee shop because it is convinient place, i can order food or drinks. It provide space to talk with friends. Sometimes, we can enjoy the music, take a photo. It creates memories last forever. 
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-42.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">2</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Socializing</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Do you prefer small or large groups?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you prefer small or large groups?
i prefer small groups. I believe that relationship is highly-demanding. It requires a lot of time, money and effort, so small group can build a stronger conection.
</p><hr></body></html>